00:00:40.080 --> 00:00:43.900
Nostalgia Critic: Hello, I'm the Nostalgia Critic, I remember it so you don't have to

00:00:43.900 --> 00:00:47.240
and welcome to the first week of Nostalgia-Ween and you know what that means?

00:00:47.240 --> 00:00:50.700
You look around in all the stores and what do you see since October...

00:00:50.700 --> 00:00:51.440
...September.

